16
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:39,300
 The curry is ready.

17
00:03:40,230 --> 00:03:42,410
 Yu Ri?

18
00:03:47,890 --> 00:03:50,460
Grandma?

19
00:03:50,460 --> 00:03:53,980
 Come on out and eat!

20
00:04:03,890 --> 00:04:06,040
 Don't skip any meals.

21
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:09,500
 I get it, I get it.

22
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:11,910
