 What about the aurora? When are you going to see that?

26
00:04:22,940 --> 00:04:26,740
 You are not even flying internationally, why are you so worried about me?

27
00:04:26,740 --> 00:04:29,570
 It's because you don't eat well by yourself.

28
00:04:29,570 --> 00:04:31,230
 Enjoy your vacation.

29
00:04:31,230 --> 00:04:35,180
 And stop worrying about your granddaughter's meals.

30
00:04:37,900 --> 00:04:41,070
 Grandma! I want to have curry, too.

31
00:04:41,070 --> 00:04:44,310
 Hey, Lee Yu Ri. Why did you take this down?

32
00:04:46,300 --> 00:04:48,560
 First, you eat well, even by yourself.

33
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:52,100
 Second, always keep yourself clean, go to bed early, and wake up early, even by yourself.

34
00:04:52,100 --> 00:04:53,990
 What's the third one? Read it out for yourself.

35
00:04:53,990 --> 00:04:55,430
 Stop it. I memorized everything already.

36
00:04:55,430 --> 00:04:57,840
 Then you tell me.

37
00:04:58,630 --> 00:05:02,930
 Third, always do your homework, even if you are alone.

38
00:05:02,930 --> 00:05:04,940
 And you didn't do your homework today.

39
00:05:04,940 --> 00:05:08,040
