42
00:05:14,220 --> 00:05:18,570
 It's written in the picture diary that we promised each other to keep it.

43
00:05:18,570 --> 00:05:20,890
 It's so childish! Why are you still talking about that old thing?

44
00:05:20,890 --> 00:05:25,410
