 What about the winter solstice?

104
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:34,140
 It's the day with the longest night, so the ghosts go around on that night.

105
00:12:34,140 --> 00:12:35,750
 What?

106
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:38,820
 Ghosts?

107
