111
00:12:59,500 --> 00:13:02,970
 Gosh! Stop it!

112
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:09,610
 Red bean soup is a food that gets rid of those ghosts.

113
00:13:09,610 --> 00:13:12,520
 So eat a lot.

114
00:13:18,890 --> 00:13:20,510
 It's hot.

115
00:13:21,210 --> 00:13:23,570
 Be careful.

116
00:13:23,570 --> 00:13:26,590
