125
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:50,920
 You are so annoying!

126
00:13:50,920 --> 00:13:54,770
 Hey, why are you two fighting over my nickname?

127
00:13:54,770 --> 00:13:57,280
 Stop fighting again, guys.

128
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:59,730
